    Process samples to a list that can be included to a dataframe

    samples_to_list.Rd

    Process samples to a list that can be included to a dataframe

    samples_to_list(object, par_name = "", n_samples = NULL)

    Arguments

    object

    Stanfit object containing variable par_name or matrix with rows representing samples, columns representing variables.

    par_name

    Name of variable to extract when object is a stanfit object.

    n_samples

    How many samples to return. Default (=NULL) to all samples.

    Value

    List of vector of samples
